  "title": "Senior Full Stack Developer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary:</strong></p><p>We are seeking a talented and highly motivated <strong>Senior Full Stack Developer to join our Custom Development Team.</strong> You will conform to high standards of code and design, working in a cutting-edge, agile, and professionally challenging environment.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>      Own end-to-end delivery including testing and bug fixing</li><li>      Participate in architecture and system design activities</li><li>     Be deeply hands-on in code and follow software development best practice</li><li>     Work   in an Agile environment (using SCRUM)</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>·       At least 5 years of experience as a Full-Stack developer</p><p>·       At least 3 years of experience with Back-End development</p><p>·       At least 3 years of experience as a Front-End developer</p><p>·      Strong experience with one Object-oriented backend ecosystem <strong>(.Net8, Java/Spring, C++…)</strong></p><p>·      Proficiency in front-end development using <strong>Typescript (React,Vue, or Angular)</strong></p><p>·       Experience with<strong> Agentic AI concepts and tech is a strong advantage</strong></p><p>·       Experience in working with/fora lab or an innovation group is an advantage</p>",
